ter.com/carlquintanilla/status/1765908327639179307">独立于能源</a>。但更重要的是太阳能和电池成本的<a href="https://twitter.com/threekardashevs/status/1766264117634195895">大幅下降</a>。近一个世纪以来，我们发现新的能源技术比旧能量技术更好。因此，全世界都以加速的速度安装了大量的太阳能和电池，这一点不足为奇。当然，中国是这方面的领头羊，但美国也<a href="https://www.nathanielbullard.com/presentations">进行了大量投资</a>——建设太阳能工厂、购买电动汽车和建设电池工厂。</p><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/repost-why-im-so-excited-about-solar">我对此感到兴奋的</a>原因 - 为什么您也应该兴奋 - 是<em>生产力</em>。就在1970年代初美国生产率增长放缓的时候，石油冲击使我们<a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/making-energy-too-cheap-to-meter/">开始减少能源使用</a>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F41ce0056-f84f-466e-bed3-f68a32a0dc97_915x528.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F41ce0056-f84f-466e-bed3-f68a32a0dc97_915x528.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F41ce0056-f84f-466e-bed3-f68a32a0dc97_915x528.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F41ce0056-f84f-466e-bed3-f68a32a0dc97_915x528.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F41ce0056-f84f-466e-bed3-f68a32a0dc97_915x528.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsub