wing that Trump&#39;s sway over the party may not be as absolute as believed. More likely, Trump &amp; co. simply didn&#39;t have enough time to work their magic on the opinion of the GOP base. Anyway, we&#39;ll see how the bill does in the Senate. </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/trump-just-rug-pulled-the-china-hawks?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/trump-just-rug-pulled-the-china-hawks?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p></p>; 
